  "couplingIntensity": "Moderate",
  "description": "Osprey's coastal tidal frequency — drawn from the ShoreSystem's geological data — modulates OHM's commune tuning reference. The coastline becomes the commune's pitch fork. As the shore frequency shifts across Osprey's five-coastline system, the drone recenters itself around that new geological keynote. ModToMod coupling: osprey_shoreBlend → ohm_tuning, amount 0.68. The hippy dad finally tunes to the land, not the grid.",
